songs.title: Seventeen
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Ooh, ooh
Ooh, ooh (Yeah, yeah)
Ooh, ooh (Woo)
Wassup
Wassup
Wassup
Wassup, yeah

[Chorus: ZillaKami]
Morgue in the, pits we torment ya
Inside a, way in the center
Drugs in me, might lose my temper
Magazine, we gonna get you up
Morgue in the, pits we torment ya
Inside a, way in the center
Drugs in me, might lose my temper
Magazine, we gonna get you up

[Verse: ZillaKami]
Suburban kid
Bang my head, 'til the brain, bust
Drink, one, fifty, one, proof
Kill my taste buds
Who the fuck is you?
Runnin' down, we don't play stuff
Who the fuck is you?
Runnin' down, we don't play stuff
Uh, lil' Godzilla dipped out the bank in a mask
Ran off of the cops, sayin', looked at the Jag
And with the panic provider, react that fast
Smoke [?] my nose, [?] pressin' the gas, fuck
Dipped out and then I pop the clutch
The middle finger out the window, I give two fucks
I shot fire, and now I gotta roll and duck
And now [?], now I gotta bust, bust, bust, bust

[Chorus: ZillaKami]
Morgue in the, pits we torment ya
Inside a, way in the center
Drugs in me, might lose my temper
Magazine, we gonna get you up
Morgue in the, pits we torment ya
